snippet.title: Animators Hell | Twisted 25
snippet.description:
I love this game so much. It's challenging, fun, and fair. It looks stunning. Everything is unique. It really just feels like the perfect fangame. Good job to everyone who has helped to work on it, and good luck to those who think they are a match for the Twisted 25

Game - https://gamejolt.com/games/animatorshell2/445906

0:00 - Intro
0:41 - Deth lol
1:08 - Winning Run
7:21 - Win Screen
8:16 - Outro

Donate if you want for some reason - https://streamlabs.com/frogger25ttv
